- 法兰克，我是苏西，莎拉的朋友  - 苏西？你好
- Frank, this is Suzy. Sara's friend?  - Suzy? Hello?

683
01:17:33,910 --> 01:17:36,410
- 我不能…  - 说大声一点，我不能听得很清楚
- I can't...  - Talk louder. I can't hear you very well.

684
01:17:36,410 --> 01:17:39,910
- 有什么事吗？ - 我还没听到莎拉的消息
- Did something happen?  - Well, I haven't heard from Sara,

685
01:17:39,910 --> 01:17:42,910
但有很多奇怪的事情在发生
But a lot of strange things are happening.

686
