哈罗？哈罗，法兰克？
Hello? Hello, Frank?

688
01:17:50,120 --> 01:17:53,000
哈罗？你听到吗？
Hello? Can you hear me?

689
01:17:53,000 --> 01:17:55,910
法兰克？哈罗？
Frank? Hello?

690
01:17:55,910 --> 01:17:59,240
哈罗？哈罗？
Hello? Hello?

691
01:17:59,240 --> 01:18:01,240
哈罗？
Hello?

692
01:18:02,750 --> 01:18:06,240
哈罗，法兰克，你听到吗？
Hello, Frank, can you hear me?

693
