不！
No!

694
01:19:43,740 --> 01:19:46,740
不！
No!

695
01:21:28,150 --> 01:21:31,650
她们根本没有离开学校
They don't leave the school at all.

696
01:21:31,650 --> 01:21:36,610
前门在左边，她们的脚步声往右边走
The front door is on the left. Their footsteps are going to the right.

697
