二、三、四、五、六…
Two, three, four, five, six,

698
01:22:09,610 --> 01:22:12,570
七…
Seven...

699
01:22:15,070 --> 01:22:20,070
只要数出她们的脚步，我就可以找到她们去哪里
I can find out where they're going by counting their footsteps.

700
01:23:32,560 --> 01:23:34,560
二十步
Twenty.

701
01:24:45,730 --> 01:24:48,230
谁在那里？
Who's there?

702
01:25:30,560 --> 01:25:34,390
地毯，这就是为什么脚步声会在这里停止
Carpet. That's why the footsteps stop here.

703
01:25:52,810 --> 01:25:56,300
这是不可能的，应该有其他的路离开这里
It's impossible. There's gotta be another way out of here.

704
01:27:04,840 --> 01:27:07,600
秘密…我在门的后面看到！
The secret... I saw it behind the door!

705
